BACKTESTING PROMPT

    backtest with a date range that includes both ticker fetching and market regime analysis:
        python your_script_name.py --backtest-range YYYY-MM-DD:YYYY-MM-DD
    For example, to run a backtest for the entire year of 2020:
        python market_regime_scanner.py --backtest-range 2020-01-01:2020-12-31
    Or for a specific month:
        python market_regime_scanner.py --backtest-range 2020-03-01:2020-03-31
    List available backtest dates:
        python market_regime_scanner.py --list-backtests
    List available backtest years:
        python market_regime_scanner.py --list-backtest-years
    Show results for a specific backtest date:
        python market_regime_scanner.py --show-backtest-results 2020-03-15
    Show analysis for a specific backtest date:
        python market_regime_scanner.py --show-backtest-analysis 2020-03-15
    Run backtest for a specific year:
        python market_regime_scanner.py --backtest-year 2020